  "subject": "Publish snapshots on merge (instead of releases)",
  "commit_message": "Publish snapshots on merge (instead of releases)\n\n- currently each merge attempts to publish the jar artifact\n  of this repo to the maven releases repo in nexus.onap.org\n- this CR changes the default behaviour to publish -SNAPSHOT\n  jars to the snapshot repo in nexus\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-173\nChange-Id: I138a7104e48be922f070e51e6a581cb464f7fc69\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
